</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Hood lock member, lamp support member and lamp support brace 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B06001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Front fender lower bracket 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Cowl side outer member 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B06005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Dash side front panel with cowl top side front panel 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B06006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
