<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9B06003001">
<title>
General Notes
</title>
<ptxt>
Welding method and number of welding points are the same on both sides. This repair instruction shows procedure for left side.
</ptxt>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9B06003002">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drill out welding spots and remove apron side member.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0011.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "196.851mm" ver = "06" gw = "496" gh = "541"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.466in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.630in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Grind welding spots using belt sander, if necessary.
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A9B06003003">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Before conducting any weld, check installation position and condition for installation part(s). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B04004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 / 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B04009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Proceed repair while taking into consideration installation of parts that affect appearance. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9B04003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install apron side member.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Conduct resistance spot weld and plug weld.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A9B0012.jpg" width = "183.000mm" height = "196.851mm" ver = "04" gw = "492" gh = "541"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
